description: hi there! this is my playlist

movies.title: Joker
movies.summaryInfo: During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.

movies.title: Maleficent: Mistress of Evil
movies.summaryInfo: Maleficent and her goddaughter Aurora begin to question the complex family ties that bind them as they are pulled in different directions by impending nuptials, unexpected allies, and dark new forces at play.

movies.title: Gemini Man
movies.summaryInfo: Henry Brogen, an aging assassin tries to get out of the business but finds himself in the ultimate battle: fighting his own clone who is 25 years younger than him and at the peak of his abilities.

movies.title: Rambo: Last Blood
movies.summaryInfo: When John Rambo's niece travels to Mexico to find the father that abandoned her and her mother, she finds herself in the grasps of Calle Mexican sex traffickers. When she doesn't return home as expected, John learns she's crossed into Mexico and sets out to get her back and make them pay.

movies.title: Hustlers
movies.summaryInfo: A crew of savvy former strip club employees band together to turn the tables on their Wall Street clients.
